quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  11,38,"Homo moЖҙЖҙina laana kan. Tuma kala nde dental hoorewal rewi ka o moЖҙЖҙinta ton, Й“e jalkita mo. o maaki: "Si on jalkitii men, minen kadi min njalkitoyay on wano njalkitirton [men non]"."
  11,39,"Arma nde ngannduЙ—on ko hommbo lepte koynatЙ—e aroyat e muuЙ—um, lepte duumiiЙ—e njippoo e makko."
  11,40,"Haa si yamiroore amen nden aroyii, huЙ“Й“inirЙ—e Й—en fati, min daali: "Roondo e makka kala nooneeji Й—iЙ—i resindirayЙ—i e Й“eynguure maa nden -si wanaa Й“en konngol lepte ngol adii e mu'un- e Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e". GoosЙ—inaano won`dude e makko si wonah seeЙ—aaЙ“e."
  11,41,"O maaki: "mbaЙ—Й—ee e makka e Innde Alla ka dogugol makka e daragol makko. Pellet Joomi am ko kaforoowo jurmotooЙ—o"."
  11,42,"Kan no dogida e maЙ“Й“e e mollooЙ—e waaЙ—e wa pelle. Nuuhu noddi Й“iЙ—Й—o makko on, hari on no serindi: "eehey ma yo Й“inngel am, waЙ—Й—ida e amen, wata a wonВҙdu e yedduЙ“e Й“een"."
  11,43,"O wi'i: "Mi Жҙawoyay e fello daЙ—ndayngo kam ndiyam Й—am". O maaki: "DaЙ—oowo yamiroore Alla nden alaa hannde si wanah oon Mo O yurmini". Molloonde nden heedi hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, o laatodii e yoolaaЙ“e Й“en."
  11,44,"Wi'a: "eeyma leydi, moЙ— ndiyam maa Й—am! eeyma kadi yo kammu, jogito [sorombooji ndiyam Й—in]!". Ndiyam Й—am Й“eeЙ“i, fiyaaku on Гұaawaa, [laana] kan daroyii ka dow fello juudiiy, wi'aa: "Halkaare woodanii Й“en yimЙ“e tooГұЙ“e"."
  11,45,"Nuuhu noddi Joomi makko, o maaki: "Joomi am, pellet Й“iЙ—Й—o am on ko jeyaaЙ—o e Й“eynguure am, pellet fodoore maa nde ko goonga. Ko aan Й“uri nuunЙ—ude Гұaawoore ГұaawooЙ“e"."